{"tid":687707,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【M巾劏盤】嫌等太耐閃人 代理反鬧客「無錢唔好扮有錢」","createTime":"2018-06-02T13:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T10:04:33.000Z","uid":83582,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e375ff43267009baaabc604ca1ab87006217dbbc","tid":687707,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"2018年06月02日 <br />\n<br />\n恒地（012）大角嘴劏房盤利奧坊．凱岸今日首度開放示位，予公眾參觀，並於明日起收票，發展商稱預計最快下周末開售。<br />\n<br />\n下午3時許，記者在售樓廠現場所見，有長人龍等候睇示範單位，各年齡層都有，當中不乏情侶檔。本身居住在南區竹睇樓客張太太認為，樓盤位置近地鐵站及所屬區份好，所以感興趣，打算買入1個1房單位作投資用，還透露自己手持多個物業收租用。被問到會否擔心樓價跌及加息等，她指「樓市跌就唔好放，守住佢！就實得架啦，最緊要有錢守住。」<br />\n<br />\n期後，現場突然起混亂，多名代理叫囂，並圍着一對疑似夫婦睇樓客，幸有保安出手護着該對夫婦離去，不過仍有代理大罵「無錢就唔好扮有錢買樓」、「買樓唔洗排隊架」等表達不滿，其後向保安了解事件，相信是因為睇樓等候時間太長，所以失去耐性而離去。<br />\n<br />\n記者︰葉煜燊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180602/large/1527927078_ca60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180602%2Flarge%2F1527927078_ca60.jpg&h=ffd4cf66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180602/58269182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58269182&d=MByN8l5tr7paOzoQpA3Ku0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=2ba6f0a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58269182&h=763ae50c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180602/58269182</a>"},{"pid":"128197f8f3d2858b7467df3086e64966cf98e97f","tid":687707,"uid":42820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"地產狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a32d44bdb62a3baec21b234577635cf7310053","tid":687707,"uid":40397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:12:34